      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in roadworthy shape. It will require significant mechanical repairs, including engine diagnostics and likely a transmission replacement, as well as extensive bodywork to address heavy rust and multiple dents. The interior shows substantial wear with several tears in the upholstery and some non-functional dashboard components. This is strictly a project vehicle for someone looking to restore it or use it for parts, and it is sold as-is.",
