      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and reliability, having been meticulously maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals the minor, honest road wear expected of a car that\u2019s been enjoyed. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing, and every button and feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has received regular synthetic oil changes and recent brake service, ensuring the engine pulls strong and the transmission shifts with precision. Sold with a clean title and a documented service history, this is a dependable, high-quality driver\u2019s car ready for its next chapter.",
